Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:58.25,1080CN_UPPER,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&}红色牌子上写 限制区域 闲人免进\N{\c&H00FFFF&}黄色牌子上写 乘组更衣室只供宇航员使用 此区域正在被监控
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:43.27,1080CN_UPPER,,0,0,0,,标签上印着“天际线飞船宇航员”\N飞船图标下方是频道名“每日宇航员”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.42,1080CN_UPPER,,0,0,0,,辣鸡波音吃枣药丸！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:07.90,1080CN_UPPER,,0,0,0,,疯狂暗示太空叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.45,1080CN_UPPER,,0,0,0,,还有充电的同学们
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.12,0:00:02.52,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,大家吼，我是《每日宇航员》频道的Tim Dodd
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.12,0:00:02.52,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Hi, it's me, Tim Dodd, the Everyday Astronaut.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.71,0:00:09.34,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我2013年开始就在节目里穿着这件有股怪味的毛子高空飞行服了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.71,0:00:09.34,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I've owned this horrendously smelly and well-worn Russian high-altitude flight suit since 2013.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.92,0:00:13.44,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你要问我为啥买这东西，我只能回答你无可奉告
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.92,0:00:13.44,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Why did I buy it? Well, I have no idea.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.68,0:00:15.26,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,就算它有一次差点杀了我
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.68,0:00:15.26,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,After it almost killed me
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.36,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我还是穿着它环游了世界还拍了很多酷炫的照片
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.36,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I still continued to take it around the world with me to take whimsical photographs.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.26,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而录节目的时候它简直就是我的负担
Dialogue: 2,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.26,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,And now, it's basically the bane of my existence.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.84,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,尽管我对这件沙雕衣服又爱又恨
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.84,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Then although I have a love-hate relationship with this stupid thing,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.24,0:00:32.16,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我还是不知道它在紧急失压时是如何工作的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.24,0:00:32.16,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I do question how well would it actually work in the event of a sudden spontaneous decompression.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.68,0:00:37.16,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得我该研究研究真正的宇航服并试穿一下
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.68,0:00:37.16,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,So, I think it's time I check out a real spacesuit, try it on
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.26,0:00:42.80,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,决定是否把这件收好吃灰，然后了解一哈某款蓝色的宇航服
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.26,0:00:42.80,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and see if it's worth hanging up the old worn spacesuit for something a little more blue.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.00,0:00:43.72,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,走你！
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.00,0:00:43.72,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.25,0:00:58.58,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到德州休斯敦，NASA约翰逊宇航中心
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.25,0:00:58.58,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Houston, Texas, home of NASA's Johnson Space Center
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.62,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这里我将给你们看些一颗赛艇的好东西
Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.62,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and I'm here to show you guys something really exciting.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.39,0:01:10.14,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,波音请了我和我的团队来这里了解一下美国的新一代航天服
Dialogue: 2,0:01:05.39,0:01:10.14,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Boeing flew me and my crew out to check out one of America's next spacesuits.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.14,0:01:12.69,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这是全新的两件宇航服之一
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.14,0:01:12.69,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,This is one of two brand new spacesuits
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.69,0:01:17.82,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,NASA新一代宇航员将穿着它在2019年前往太空
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.69,0:01:17.82,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,that a new generation of astronauts will be wearing to Space in 2019.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.82,0:01:22.98,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,前不久NASA刚刚公布首批商业载人飞行首飞乘组
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.82,0:01:22.98,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,In case you missed it, NASA just announced who will be flying on these first Commercial Crew flights,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.98,0:01:30.32,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,波音和太空叉都在比谁的飞船、发射场、航天服先准备好
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.98,0:01:30.32,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and both Boeing and SpaceX are racing to get their spaceships, their launch sites, and their spacesuits ready
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.43,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,让美国人重返太空
Dialogue: 2,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.43,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,to return humans to Space from US soil.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.43,0:01:39.56,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,虽然我本人没经过任何航天方面的训练（我觉得玩KSP不算）
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.43,0:01:39.56,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Despite having virtually zero training, since I doubt playing lots of Kerbal Space Program counts,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.56,0:01:43.25,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,波音还是邀请我体验他们最先进的宇航服
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.56,0:01:43.25,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I've been asked to check out Boeing's super advanced spacesuit.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.25,0:01:48.53,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,在期待了很久之后，我终于穿上了宇航服的内衬
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.25,0:01:48.53,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,After much anticipation, it's time to put on some space underwear.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.09,0:01:58.10,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我真幸运呀，我现在应该算官方钦点宇航员了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.09,0:01:58.10,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Well, lucky for me, I guess I'm now officially considered an astronaut.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.57,0:02:01.85,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,太空忍（沙）者（雕）！
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.57,0:02:01.85,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Space ninja!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.20,0:02:05.34,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,宇航服时间！液！
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.20,0:02:05.34,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Spacesuit time! Yeah!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.12,0:02:09.68,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,简直帅呆了！太……
Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.12,0:02:09.68,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,This is awesome! This is so...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.84,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们能换一件吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.84,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Can we switch suits?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.00,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,有没有机会……
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.00,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Is there a chance that...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.78,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,能让我花钱把这买下来呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.78,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Like how can I please just purchase one of these?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.10,0:02:20.13,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这和我想象中的21世纪的宇航服差不多
Dialogue: 2,0:02:16.10,0:02:20.13,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is what I think of when I think of a 21st century suit,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.48,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,各种东西变小变轻
Dialogue: 2,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.48,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,like something actually lightweight and small.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.87,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,在了解更多有关宇航服的信息之前
Dialogue: 2,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.87,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Before I could prod too much at the suit,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.67,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,波音的飞行乘组操作与测试工程师
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.67,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Boeing's flight crew operations and test engineer,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.67,0:02:31.96,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,KKM要先来给我们补补课
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.67,0:02:31.96,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Kavya Kamal Manyapu, came over to answer all my questions,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.60,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,就在这时我发现了什么
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.60,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and that's when I noticed something.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.92,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,等下，我发现……你快来看看这个！
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.92,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Wait, I just read... Come here, look at this!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.47,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我勒个去！
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.47,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.47,0:02:43.27,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你们……天啊……流批！
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.47,0:02:43.27,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,You guys! Look at that! What!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.70,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你们快把我感动哭了，太牛逼了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.70,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,You guys are gonna end up making me cry here. That's amazing!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.24,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,哭吧，我们是见得多了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.24,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We get that a lot, so you can cry.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.58,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你这还有人哭？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.58,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,You have people weeping?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.86,0:03:01.15,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们的航天服是有多年宇航服设计经验的David Clark设计的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.86,0:03:01.15,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Our spacesuit is built by David Clark that have many several years of experience in actually building spacesuits
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.15,0:03:05.45,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,他参与了阿波罗工程开始到之前的航天飞机任务
Dialogue: 2,0:03:01.15,0:03:05.45,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,starting from Apollo and even the recent Space Shuttle.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.77,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,就是宇航员穿的橙色的那件——
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.77,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,What you see the orange suits that the astronauts wear--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.58,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,嗯，就是“南瓜装”嘛
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.58,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,The pumpkin suit, lovingly called.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.04,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们这里的设计叫“软兜帽”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.04,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,So, we have what's called a soft-hood.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.48,0:03:18.67,1080CN_BELOW,,0,800,0,,你的那件高空飞行服脖子上有个圈对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.48,0:03:18.67,1080CN_BELOW,,1200,0,0,,对，老难受了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.48,0:03:18.67,1080EN_BELOW,,0,800,0,,You have a neck ring on your spacesuit
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.48,0:03:18.67,1080EN_BELOW,,1200,0,0,,Yes, it's the worse thing in the entire world.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.98,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,想象你穿着这个，就像个兜帽一样
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.98,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Imagine wearing this, it's like a hoodie.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.98,0:03:21.83,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,哇天啊
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.98,0:03:21.83,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.83,0:03:24.51,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,所以这就很方便穿脱
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.83,0:03:24.51,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,So, it's like really easy to don and doff.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.58,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Doff是个词？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.58,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Doff is a word?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.51,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.51,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Doff is a word.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.68,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,刚来这么一会就学到这么多
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.68,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm learning so much already.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.14,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,但这仅仅是开始
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.14,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,But that was just the beginning.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.40,0:03:36.06,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我发现这件衣服比上一代轻了40%
Dialogue: 2,0:03:31.40,0:03:36.06,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I found out the suit is 40% lighter than all previous generation suits.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.84,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,尽管衣服变轻，而且使用的是更方便的拉链式头盔
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.84,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Despite being lightweight and featuring that easy to zip helmet,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.84,0:03:43.38,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这件衣服却能承受内部3.5PSI的压强(24kPa)
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.84,0:03:43.38,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,the suit can hold an internal pressure of 3.5 PSI
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.59,0:03:48.84,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,大约相当于一万米或者三万四千英尺高度的气压
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.59,0:03:48.84,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,which is the same amount of air you'd have at 10,000 meters or at 34,000 feet in altitude.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.84,0:03:54.63,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,更厉害的是手套在完全充气以后仍能保证灵活性
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.84,0:03:54.63,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,And most impressively, the gloves maintain their dexterity even when fully inflated, as well.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.46,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这是很难做到的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.46,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That's the challenge.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.46,0:04:00.16,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,航天服手套的设计是极难的，里面有很多灵活设计
Dialogue: 2,0:03:55.46,0:04:00.16,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,They actually say that the gloves are the hardest thing to design, and these look really, really slick.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.78,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这……你看它多薄啊
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.78,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,This is... Look at how thin they are.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.78,0:04:05.61,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你们见没见过阿波罗里的舱外宇航服
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.78,0:04:05.61,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,You guys have probably seen like the shots of Apollo gloves.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.61,0:04:09.55,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,那大老粗手指
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.61,0:04:09.55,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Those EVA suits have these huge, crazy, puffy fingers,
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.55,0:04:13.21,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,简直天壤之别，太厉害了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.55,0:04:13.21,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and this is the exact opposite of that. That's amazing.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.35,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,不过当然我要说明一点
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.35,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,But here's where I should offer up some quick clarification.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.02,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这是舱内宇航服
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.02,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,This is a flight suit,
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.68,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,只在飞船内部穿的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.68,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,which is really only worn inside a spacecraft,
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.98,0:04:24.80,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,比如飞往空间站途中与返回地球途中
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.98,0:04:24.80,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,like when you actually fly to the International Space Station or return home.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.80,0:04:28.28,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,宇航员还是需要全套舱外宇航服
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.80,0:04:28.28,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Astronauts will still have to wear a full extravehicular activity suit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.46,0:04:31.66,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,舱外航天服自带生命保障系统与冷却系统
Dialogue: 2,0:04:28.46,0:04:31.66,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,which have their own life-support systems and cooling systems built in
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.40,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,供他们太空行走时使用
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.40,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,if they need to go on a spacewalk
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.61,0:04:37.33,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而波音这件替换的是橙色的飞行服
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.61,0:04:37.33,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,but what this replaces is that orange shuttle aero flight suit.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.34,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,看看南瓜装有多臃肿吧
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.34,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,And just look at how bulky that thing was.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.34,0:04:43.94,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,是不是有种年轻人穿宽松衣服的潮流的感觉
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.34,0:04:43.94,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I guess that's about how baggy clothes were back then anyway.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.27,0:04:48.40,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,David Clark还和Reebok合作设计了这个
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.27,0:04:48.40,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,David Clark has partnered with Reebok to come up with this design.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.52,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,真的很轻
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.52,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It's really lightweight.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.02,0:04:53.80,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我滴个乖乖这也太轻了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.02,0:04:53.80,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Oh my, this is... When you say really lightweight, you're not kidding.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.82,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,轻得有点过分了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.82,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,This is crazy lightweight.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.09,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,敢问这鞋有多重？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.09,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,How heavy are these, do you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.09,0:04:58.44,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,2磅（0.9千克）
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.09,0:04:58.44,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Two pounds.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.93,0:04:59.76,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,-每个2磅？  -每双
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.93,0:04:59.76,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,- Two pounds each? - A pair.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.30,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,每双
Dialogue: 2,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.30,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,A pair.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.38,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这双鞋拿着就像是
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.38,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Both of the these feel about as light
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.15,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Toms那种鞋一样
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.15,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,as my like normal like Toms even.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.15,0:05:08.07,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我真不知道你们是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.15,0:05:08.07,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I swear I don't know how you make these that light.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.16,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,纳米碳管，我就猜是这个了！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.16,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Carbon nano-tubes. I'm calling it now.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.83,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,行了，废话少说，穿上试试吧
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.83,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Okay, enough talking about it. Let's put this thing on.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.29,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,裤腿穿进去好容易
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.29,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It slides on so easy.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.64,0:05:21.96,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我其实每次穿我那件衣服都会记着
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.64,0:05:21.96,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I might hold the record, actually, for putting on my stupid spacesuit thing.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.22,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我大概穿过一百来次
Dialogue: 2,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.22,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I've probably put that on, what, hundreds of times.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.93,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这第一次就已经比我那件还要好穿了
Dialogue: 2,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.93,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It's already much easier than my suit.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.21,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,OK，走你
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.21,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Okay, there we go.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.21,0:05:33.27,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,胳膊要这样
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.21,0:05:33.27,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Adjust the arms like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.98,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,OK，你最后要做的……
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.98,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Okay, now what you'll end up doing here...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.40,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,等我先把这边弄好
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.40,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Let me get this side squared.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.12,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,……是向前向下弯腰
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.12,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Is you are going to bend forward and down
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.01,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,脑袋穿过这里
Dialogue: 2,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.01,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and through here with your head.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.15,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,然后慢慢肩膀也跟进去
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.15,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,And slowly roll your shoulders in.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.15,0:05:48.98,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.15,0:05:48.98,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.07,0:05:55.12,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,然后你继续向前慢慢站起，我们将把屁股两侧衣服拉过来
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.07,0:05:55.12,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Now you can go ahead and slowly stand up and we'll pull this around your hips.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.10,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,哇好简单啊
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.10,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That was so easy.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.43,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,OK，向前几步
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.43,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Okay, step forward for me a couple of steps.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.65,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.65,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.65,0:06:02.90,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,两臂向两侧伸平
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.65,0:06:02.90,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Arm out to the sides.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.86,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,让我整理下褶皱部分
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.86,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm working the wrinkles out.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.86,0:06:05.70,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,感觉如何
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.86,0:06:05.70,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,How's it feel?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.53,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,爽灿了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.53,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:13.50,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我能雇你们把我的那件旧的换了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.37,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,看啊！简直不敢相信……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.11,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,太帅了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.47,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,感觉胳膊肘这地方……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.31,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,感觉像是什么也没穿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.31,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你们看！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:24.85,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,看有多灵活
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.08,0:06:28.11,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我想说，我真能穿这个在家门口遛弯
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.08,0:06:28.11,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I mean, I could actually wear this around the house.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.38,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我跟你讲我的经历
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.38,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you from experience,
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.68,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我曾经穿我那件衣服整整八小时
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.68,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I've worn my suit for like eight hours at a time,
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.05,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,简直炼狱一般
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.05,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and it's the worst thing ever.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.05,0:06:38.60,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,但这件，我能穿几个礼拜
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.05,0:06:38.60,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I could do this for weeks.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.18,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我只要把我房子卖了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.18,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'll just sell my house,
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.93,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,因为这和一个房子差不多了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.93,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,'cause this is basically like your own little house,
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.17,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,一个移动的房子
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.17,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,a mobile house.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.11,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我今天就住这里了，不脱了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.11,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'll just live in this from now on.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.11,0:06:45.94,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,快穿好啦
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.11,0:06:45.94,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.94,0:06:49.46,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这种兜帽式头盔无法在冲击发生时提供足够的保护
Dialogue: 2,0:06:45.94,0:06:49.46,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,The hoodie helmet itself doesn't offer much for crash protection,
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.46,0:06:53.71,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,所以宇航员还要戴一个内部头盔
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.46,0:06:53.71,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,so astronauts will wear a beenie that has a small built-in helmet pad
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.71,0:06:58.41,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,其上还装有通讯系统，用于与他人、地面控制中心交流
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.71,0:06:58.41,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,as well as the communications system to speak with each other and ground control.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.05,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,双麦克风！
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.05,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Dual microphones.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.60,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,小甜甜布兰妮得嫉妒死我
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.60,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Britney Spears would be very jealous.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.43,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这栗子不太好？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.43,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Is that a bad reference?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.88,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,谁穿得更潮一点？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.88,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Who's the more modern?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.23,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,嘎嘎得嫉妒死我！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.23,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Lady Gaga would be very jealous.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.46,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这也不好，嘎嘎也不用这些东西
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.46,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,No, but she doesn't use one of those things.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.54,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,谁还用？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.54,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Who else uses?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.54,0:07:12.80,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,JB？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.54,0:07:12.80,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Bieber?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.69,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,爱谁谁吧
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.69,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.69,0:07:17.13,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,反正那些穿成像这样的名人
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.69,0:07:17.13,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Insert famous person that has one of these.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.49,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,肯定都嫉妒死我了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.49,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,They're jealous right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.45,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我现在穿着全世界最先进的宇航服
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.45,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing the most advanced spacesuit in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.49,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,还有俩麦克风，我好兴♂奋呀
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.45,0:07:22.49,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and I'm excited about two microphones.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.57,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我的天！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.57,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.73,0:07:29.56,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这就行了？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.73,0:07:29.56,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.04,0:07:31.87,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.04,0:07:31.87,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.09,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,穿戴好容易啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.09,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It goes on so easy.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.76,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.76,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.76,0:07:39.94,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,请把手臂伸直
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.76,0:07:39.94,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Can you reach out completely?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.94,0:07:40.77,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.94,0:07:40.77,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.17,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,OK，网友们，能给我众筹一件吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.17,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Okay, internet, who wants to help me buy one of these?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.16,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,因为——
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.16,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Because--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.35,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这尺码挺合身的
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.35,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good length for you.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.69,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,——我现在就想要一件！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.69,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I need one of these right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.69,0:07:50.07,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我天下无敌啦！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:46.69,0:07:50.07,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I have all the power in the world!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.38,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,太爽了！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.38,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,This is so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.23,1080CN_UPPER,,0,0,0,,MDZZ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.00,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你看我牛逼不？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.00,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Do I look as cool as I feel?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.55,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你看我是不是超级牛逼？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.55,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Do I look 10 times cooler than I feel?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.78,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,因为现在就感觉我贼牛逼
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.78,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,'Cause I feel about as cool as it gets right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.07,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,在他们发现之前我能跑多远？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.07,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,How far could I get before they've noticed I ran away?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.42,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我的车停在两百米远的地方
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.42,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,The car is 200 yards that way.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.55,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我觉得我跑的比谁都快
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.55,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I think I can sprint pretty fast,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.38,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,然后我们直接开车逃跑
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.38,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and then we can drive out.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.68,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,不知道保安的车能开多快
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.68,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I don't know how fast the security cars are.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.68,0:08:20.02,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我们有辆五菱宏光，我觉得胜算很大
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.68,0:08:20.02,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,We have a Camry with a four cylinder. I think we got pretty good odds.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.02,0:08:23.80,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,在和波音媒体经理一阵谈判之后
Dialogue: 2,0:08:20.02,0:08:23.80,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,After some intense negotiations with Boeing Social Media Manager,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.80,0:08:30.19,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我突然发现自己开始尬舞了起来
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.80,0:08:30.19,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I find myself suddenly breaking into some pretty fantastic dance moves.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.42,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,为了给广大鬼畜爱好者无限想象空间
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.42,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,And just to make this 10 times better,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.86,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我决定此处不放任何音乐
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.86,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm going to leave out any music,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.87,0:08:38.27,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你们接下来听到的声音都是麦克风记录的衣服摩擦的声音
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.87,0:08:38.27,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,so all you hear is the awkward rustling of the microphone against the spacesuit.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.30,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,别这样，这段掐了别播吧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.30,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Wait, no! You're not gonna ruin me now.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.28,0:08:56.12,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,看我这样嘚瑟你们可能会问我热不
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.28,0:08:56.12,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,And here's where you might be asking is this suit hot?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.38,0:08:59.30,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,好吧，尬舞这么久之后
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.38,0:08:59.30,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Well, after dancing around in it for far too long,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.42,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,讲道理是有点热
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.42,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,yes, it does get a bit hot,
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.59,0:09:05.12,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,但幸运的是，宇航服可以连接到通风设备上
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.59,0:09:05.12,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,but luckily, the suit has an option of being hooked up to ventilation.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.19,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我一直期待这个
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.19,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That's actually what I've always wanted.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.76,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我那样尬舞其实是故意的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.76,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,This is all a big ploy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.76,0:09:11.58,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,就是为了体验一下宇航服的通风系统怎么样
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.76,0:09:11.58,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,'cause I've always wanted to see what ventilation feels like in a spacesuit
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.08,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我之前在我那件里都快热熟了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.08,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,'cause I'm used to cooking alive in spacesuits,
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.92,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而我现在也热得不行
Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.92,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,so this is nothing new.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.48,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,所以我要亲自体验一下
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.48,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,So I'm actually gonna feel
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.82,0:09:22.09,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,宇航服连上通风是什么感觉
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.82,0:09:22.09,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,what it's like to have air circulating in a spacesuit.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.64,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,感觉到循环的气流了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.64,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Feel the air circulating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.26,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,嗯感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:30.23,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,感觉就像我的私人独享空调
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.40,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,讲真我的确没必要脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.67,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我希望你们也不会强行让我脱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.90,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,现在设备都全了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.94,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,空调系统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.81,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我只要在膝盖口袋里放些饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:42.81,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我就可以住这里了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.51,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,好吧，严肃地说
Dialogue: 2,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.51,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Okay, but in all seriousness,
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.64,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,如果你看不懂我的笑容的话
Dialogue: 2,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.64,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,if you can't tell by my smile,
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.64,0:09:50.89,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,穿这件宇航服感觉很特别
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.64,0:09:50.89,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,wearing this spacesuit really feels special,
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.38,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这就是我所有的感觉
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.38,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and that's when it all sunk in.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.38,0:09:59.01,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,感觉离2011年宇航员最后一次爬进航天飞机已经过了超级久
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.38,0:09:59.01,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It feels like it's been forever since we last saw astronauts climb inside the Space Shuttle in 2011
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.98,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,当时他们还穿着鲜艳臃肿的橙色宇航服
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.98,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,wearing those iconic and bulky orange suits.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.30,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,特别有时代感
Dialogue: 2,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.30,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It feels like a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.54,0:10:08.16,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,但这件，真的很有21世纪的感觉
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.54,0:10:08.16,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,But this, this really feels 21st century,
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.96,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,更新、更高科技、更轻
Dialogue: 2,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.96,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,new, high-tech, lightweight,
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.14,0:10:15.12,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,专为新一代太空探索而准备
Dialogue: 2,0:10:11.14,0:10:15.12,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and truly ready for a new generation of Space explorers.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.82,0:10:27.81,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,不，不要……我又穿上这件旧的了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.82,0:10:27.81,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm back in this stupid thing! No!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.51,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,好吧，讲真，我要马上把这身行头换掉
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.51,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Okay, seriously, I'm going to replace this thing soon.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.36,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,穿过之后才知道波音的新宇航服有多好
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.36,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That made me realize just how much better I could actually have it.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.58,0:10:37.12,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,如果你想知道我那件衣服的由来
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.58,0:10:37.12,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,If you wanna know why I even have this spacesuit or how I got it,
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.12,0:10:41.10,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,记得看看这个视频，里面我解释了整个荒诞的来龙去脉
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.12,0:10:41.10,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,be sure and check out this video where I explain that whole ridiculous story.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.40,0:10:46.30,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,在下期视频里我将带你进入天际线飞船和训练模拟机
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.40,0:10:46.30,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,In an upcoming video, I'm going to take you inside a Starliner and the training simulator
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.70,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,让你更深入了解即将到来的商业载人航天项目
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.70,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,to help you learn even more about the upcoming Commercial Crew Program.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.60,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,感谢波音能给我们这次深入了解的机会
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.60,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Boeing for sending us down there to check out everything.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.04,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我经常这样讲
Dialogue: 2,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.04,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I say this often,
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.42,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,不要站队互喷引战
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.42,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I am not a big fan of picking teams.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.79,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,因为我只站在“探索宇宙”这一队！
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.79,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm team Let's Explore Space!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.76,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而我也要告诉你
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.76,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,But if you couldn't tell by my face,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.63,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我真的很开心
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.63,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I really had an amazing time.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.63,0:11:03.78,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,所以，感谢大家
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.63,0:11:03.78,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,So, thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.02,0:11:07.92,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,如果还有谁想让我了解你们的宇航服和飞船的话
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.02,0:11:07.92,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,If there's anyone else out there that wants me to check out their spacesuit or upcoming spaceship,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.16,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,请立即联系我
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.16,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,hit me up,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.84,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我帮你们debug！
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.84,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I definitely got the bug.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.45,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,另外我真的要好好感谢我的Patreon赞助们
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.45,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I owe a huge thanks to my Patreon supporters
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.45,0:11:16.96,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,让我不必用爱发电来做视频
Dialogue: 2,0:11:13.45,0:11:16.96,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,for helping make videos like this and all other content possible.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.22,0:11:19.27,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,为了答复你们的支持
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.22,0:11:19.27,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,As a thanks to those who support this show,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.26,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,我现在要在每100位赞助者中抽奖
Dialogue: 2,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.26,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,I'm now doing giveaways every 100 patrons.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.26,0:11:26.66,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,奖品内容是这些航天材料，比如航天飞机的一部分
Dialogue: 2,0:11:22.26,0:11:26.66,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,It'll always be some kind of lone Space material like this pieces of Space Shuttle.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.96,0:11:30.61,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,所以想得到这些硬核太空收藏品的话
Dialogue: 2,0:11:26.96,0:11:30.61,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,So if you want some chance to win some actual flown Space hardware
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.43,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,或者想去我们Reddit特别子版块的话
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.43,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,or want to hang out in our exclusive Subreddit
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.34,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,或者想进我们特别Discord频道的话
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.34,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,or our exclusive Discord channel,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.47,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,请立即去下方链接赞助我们
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.47,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,head on over to patreon.com/everdayastronaut.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.57,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,非常感谢！
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.57,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.54,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而在刷无聊的B站之余
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.54,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,And while you're out there on the grand dull internet,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.54,0:11:43.55,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,还可以去我自己的网站，链接见下
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.54,0:11:43.55,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,head on over to my website, everydayastronaut.com,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.55,0:11:48.42,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,里面有所有未来所有火箭发射的预告
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.55,0:11:48.42,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,where you can find Prelaunch Previews of all upcoming rocket launches.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.66,0:11:51.80,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,这样你们就再也不用追着屁股在推特问我
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.66,0:11:51.80,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,That's right, you finally don't have to ask me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.34,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,下次发射是什么时候什么载荷呀
Dialogue: 2,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.34,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,what's gonna happen on this upcoming mission on Twitter.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.41,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,你可以直接去我的网站就能查到
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.41,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,You can go there to my website and you can find out,
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.52,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,“这发回收吗？”
Dialogue: 2,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.52,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,"Are they gonna land this one?"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.37,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,“这发整流罩回收吗？”
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.37,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,"Is this one gonna recover a fairing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.44,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,“这发是打什么轨道呀？”
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.44,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,"Where is this mission going to?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.28,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,“这发咕到啥时候呀？”
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.28,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,"When does it launch?"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.66,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,所有这类问题都有答案
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.66,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,All the things you need to know in one easy to find place,
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.08,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,而网站里还有我的网店链接
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.08,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and then while you're there, head on over to my shop
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.46,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,看看我最新的酷炫T恤
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.46,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,and check out my new awesome shirts like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.57,0:12:14.44,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,上面印着F-1发动机哦！
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.57,0:12:14.44,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,F-1 Engine can be on your chest.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.81,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,再次重复下网址
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.81,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,everydayastronaut.com
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.47,1080CN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,感谢各位
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.47,1080EN_BELOW,,0,0,0,,Thanks everybody. That does it for me.
